# Runtime task-census cache: keep the dev's live session census out of the test
# image. Otherwise COPY . . bakes it in, the UserPromptSubmit hook (validate-specs)
# emits the FR-49a "📋 Spec tasks" banner, and specs-validator's silent-output
# assertions fail on a dirty working tree — a faked failure, not a real regression.
